241→var True, False, Nil, undefined Obj
242→var uptime time.Time
243→var symQuote, symDefun, symLambda, symFreeze, symLet, symAnd Obj
244→var symOr, symIf, symCond, symTrapError, symDo, symMacroExpand Obj
